reviews.review_msg: Year isn't finished yet but this is sort of ridiculous. I was really excited to learn, and incredibly disappointed to find out that we were teaching ourselves. It's either an absent prof missing a full month of lectures or having us do one and a half hour presentations to teach ourselves everytime. The assignments are also insanely unclear.
super nice person, not a great prof. everything was extremely disorganized and little to no explanation for anything was given. easier class for sure but be prepared to be confused
